title: onnx
description: `onnx` is a **lightweight Pure Data external** that lets you run [ONNX](https://onnx.ai/onnx/intro/) models directly inside Pd. Its small size makes it particularly suitable for **pd4web** projects where minimal memory footprint and minimal size are essential.

videos.title: Timbre Recognition in ONNX: Demo with Pd (Pure Data) & py4pd
